{"tid":764533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真‧夜王】日本最強牛郎年賺3億日元　氹掂客人呢招最緊要","createTime":"2018-08-02T05:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T09:58:03.000Z","uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d04224c4e87f5f13dcb26aacd409467f9a88759f","tid":764533,"uid":162409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1701414/org/364300faca3e4f4b088eba4c3e21c62e.jpg/6qzVghqhwXDLb5V0u-FM1Fuf8EaRzuCqnB7r95we6_c?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1701414%2Forg%2F364300faca3e4f4b088eba4c3e21c62e.jpg%2F6qzVghqhwXDLb5V0u-FM1Fuf8EaRzuCqnB7r95we6_c%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=0d426afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本的牛郎行業發展蓬勃，不少影視作品都以此為題材，但現實中的牛郎是否如鏡頭所呈現般風流快活又賺大錢呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1699275/org/742f4292f822a262cc570af7119803e3.jpg/tqWTsJwUYrgXbWtb6hDQEfawoBQoFu6TJnIxWyZyMVs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1699275%2Forg%2F742f4292f822a262cc570af7119803e3.jpg%2FtqWTsJwUYrgXbWtb6hDQEfawoBQoFu6TJnIxWyZyMVs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ae582a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯定不是所有牛郎都能夠闖出名堂，但這位「全日本第一牛郎」應該是業界的模範人物，年賺2000萬港元的他，每日花近3萬港元租住酒店套房，仲一炮過拿出280萬港元買下名車勞斯萊斯，原來賣藝不賣身都可以成為「鴨王」，究竟有咩獨門冧女秘技？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1699253/org/978bec86fc17015e29b82d1325b0059e.jpg/5vgO9ivxqakBg6XS6hzG9vjzj5o6A5TNVBScplQUnKY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1699253%2Forg%2F978bec86fc17015e29b82d1325b0059e.jpg%2F5vgO9ivxqakBg6XS6hzG9vjzj5o6A5TNVBScplQUnKY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0679242a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的ROLAND於東京出生，他在官方網站的個人簡介中，自稱18歲高中畢業後，大學都唔讀就加入牛郎行列，年僅20歲就成為歌舞伎町的牛郎店話事人，2013年獲另一牛郎店KG-produce以破紀錄薪酬挖角，去年營業額高達1.7億日元（約1200萬港元），現在ROLAND已成為KG-produce的董事之一，而他亦以專欄作家及模特兒自居。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1699347/org/ddd52d50f92132973345ae0f28302959.jpeg/TRhutxGvcxm97uulc6uC72cgNQfEd7_0K1aDDStWgw0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1699347%2Forg%2Fddd52d50f92132973345ae0f28302959.jpeg%2FTRhutxGvcxm97uulc6uC72cgNQfEd7_0K1aDDStWgw0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ce059aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1699353/org/5bc2d020ea8ef203f506622a4f7f9210.jpg/13Fsf_eN_3O9WQU9FycL63uHe7JWWGTTZK75GWSu-Rk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1699353%2Forg%2F5bc2d020ea8ef203f506622a4f7f9210.jpg%2F13Fsf_eN_3O9WQU9FycL63uHe7JWWGTTZK75GWSu-Rk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=219c3b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1699292/org/afd516974f3cc2022a676dd01c80a80f.jpg/ymItsGeUQYbmcmCRdIQwn5hMlOGEPzLjomO0yKJjtMg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1699292%2Forg%2Fafd516974f3cc2022a676dd01c80a80f.jpg%2FymItsGeUQYbmcmCRdIQwn5hMlOGEPzLjomO0yKJjtMg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=87e31b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/216839/%E7%9C%9F-%E5%A4%9C%E7%8E%8B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E7%89%9B%E9%83%8E%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA3%E5%84%84%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83-%E6%B0%B9%E6%8E%82%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%A2%E6%8B%9B%E6%9C%80%E7%B7%8A%E8%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F216839%2F%25E7%259C%259F-%25E5%25A4%259C%25E7%258E%258B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2589%259B%25E9%2583%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25BA3%25E5%2584%2584%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%25B0%25B9%25E6%258E%2582%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2591%25A2%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%259C%2580%25E7%25B7%258A%25E8%25A6%2581&d=y9KBTwxd%2BVFK6stHYWMMTgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c175